Wow the rain finally stopped but not before the flood started around here.
Spent all day trying to help friends move there livestock out of flood water also trying to get them to evacuate there property but they will wait till it is up to the house before they will go.
National guard came in to help evacuate the people in town but I guess they don't think of the country people.
Daughter stuff in storage just under about 15 feet of water poor girl may have to start all over,but daughter and granddaughter safe.I enjoyed the moose thanks.

After spending my entire life being a bug buffet I have finally found a bug stopper that works for me ,water,eucalyptus oil and lavendar oil not a bite so far after using it.Thought some of you who will be playing outside this summer would enjoy my new found knowledge.
OH yes and don't faint over the two entries in one night.PLEASE!

Roses are brown grass is white looks like I am in for a long April night!
